General.Name: Shenzhen Jove Enterprise Co. Ltd.
General.Description: Shenzhen Jove Enterprise Limited engages in the research and development, production, and sales of printed circuit boards (PCB) in China. The company offers multilayer PCBs, which are used in power control systems, servers, electric vehicles, medical devices, and 5g base stations; high density PCBs; flexible and rigid-flex products, which provide a solution for the integration of multiple rigid circuit board assemblies into a single board; substrate like PCBs for smartphones and tablets; insulated metallic substrate PCBs; and antenna/RF PCBs. It offers its products to communication, new energy, industrial control, consumer electronics, automotive electronics, medical electronics, and other application fields. The company exports its products to Europe, Asia, the United States, and internationally. Shenzhen Jove Enterprise Limited was founded in 2004 and is based in Shenzhen, China.
